The professor went over logistics. I believe he said there will be a webcast but I think he also said he needs to talk to whoever manages it to make sure. I don't think it is particularly critical that you missed the first lecture. The most important thing that they said is that for this class they want you to "shop" for your favorite discussion section. A few weeks into the semester we will then provide a list of our preferred section and they will attempt to assign everyone the highest preferences possible. From that point on you will be in that assigned section.
